data.description: Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac next to a beautiful golf course, this home has it all.  3 large bedrooms and 2.5 baths located on the main floor sitting on top of a fully finished basement with plenty of space to entertain.  The all-season sunroom, along with a deck, overlooks the partially wooded full acre lot making it perfect for watching the sunrise through the trees.  In the oversized 2 car garage you will find plenty of room for storage and a new water filtration system.  Recent updates include newer roof and appliances.
